  <ul compact><li><a href="3437.html" name="LOC_P21_1150">3437.670   Contract type.</a></li></ul></ul><hr size="2" width="80%"><!-- TRANSIT - TEXTBAR --><p><a name="P0_0"></a><b>PART 3437—SERVICE CONTRACTING</b></p>

<p><b>Section Contents</b></p>

